{{Top|leg}}
The '''University of Charmath''', located on the [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Charmath]], boasted one of the most complete historical libraries including a medical [[Laboratory/Legends|laboratory]] with the most detailed medical records throughout the known [[Galaxy/Legends|galaxy]].<ref name="Education">{{TORcite|type=crewskill|Bioanalysis|Higher Education}}</ref>

==History==
Early in the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], [[Major/Legends|Major]] [[Arhul Hextrophon/Legends|Arhul Hextrophon]], a historian for the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]], found evidence there that renowned [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[Yoda/Legends|Yoda]] was alive on [[Dagobah/Legends|Dagobah]]. He later destroyed that evidence in order to protect the secret of the Jedi Master's existence.

